docs.text:
Welcome to the LiquiDOS Docs!


Welcome to the LiquiDOS official documentation! YAY! Now what?


Project folder:  
kernelsrc








Folder/File Name


Description










boot


Contains the GRUB multiboot assembly file.






grub


Has the GRUB iso config number.






include


Contains all the C headers for the kernel.






isodir


Don't touch if you don't know what  you're doing. Used for grub iso generation.






kernel


Contains all the kernel source code.






obj


Used to store object files during compilation.






Makefile


Used to compile the kernel






linker.ld


Linker script for the linker






setenv.sh


Sets up the environment for you






build.sh


Builds the kernel (make clean && make)
